reviews.review_text: excellent recording!  hot show! Very high energy show.  Really unique He's Gone jam; sounds like they are going back into Bird Song.

very hot sh0w The Hartford Civic Center was electric that night and the crowd was loud and rode every note. Listen to the welcome Jerry gets for his first guitar solo in Midnight Hour and his first vocal in Cold Rain and Snow. China Cat is superb. Bird Song is superb. He's Gone with the meow guitar twang and the syncopated vocals to end it. Really a great Hartford Show.
